code: String toAsciidocTable() {     final StringBuilder builder = new StringBuilder().     builder.append("[cols=\"1,1,2\", options=\"header\"]").append(NEWLINE).     builder.append("|===").append(NEWLINE).append("|Key|Default Value|Description").append(NEWLINE).append(NEWLINE).     this.entries.forEach((entry) -> {         entry.writeAsciidoc(builder).         builder.append(NEWLINE).     }).     return builder.append("|===").append(NEWLINE).toString(). }
